---
title: Sticky Jerk Beef & Pork Rissoles & Carrot Couscous with Corn Salsa & Garlic Aioli
description: We’ve got a special glaze for tonight’s rissoles - an onion chutney, dark and sweet for the Caribbean spiced beef and pork. Pile them onto a bright carrot couscous with a charred corn salsa accompaniment.
